These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: lily, dahlia, daffodil, begonia, poppy, marigold, iris
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, oliveros, montecristo, bluemaster, dannemann, fonseca, game
There are 7 different favourite colors: brown, aquamarine, mauve, ebony, azure, chestnut, ivory
 1. the person who growspoppy is on the far left##1
 2. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who growslily##1
 3. the person who likes ivory is between the oliveros-smoker and the bolivar-smoker##2
 4. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
 5. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
 6. the person who growslily is the person who likes ivory##1
 7. the bluemaster-smoker is between the person who likes ebony and the person who growspoppy##2
 8. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
 9. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
10. the person who growsiris is the montecristo-smoker##1
11. the fonseca-smoker is the person who growsbegonia##1
12. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
13. the person who likes brown is the dannemann-smoker##1
14. the person who growsmarigold is between the person who likes mauve and the person who likes ivory##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Flower   | poppy | lily     | marigold | dahlia | begonia | iris  | daffodil  |
| Cigar   | bolivar  | bluemaster        | oliveros  | game     | fonseca   | montecristo       | dannemann   |
| Color         | aquamarine   | ivory | ebony    | mauve  | azure | chestnut | brown |

