.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-2::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: country, trance, ambient, funk, salsa, rock, techno
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: bellflower, iris, rose, daisy, orchid, balloon-flower, sunflower
The people have 7 different jobs:  electrician, mechanic, fisherman, doctor, freelancer, chef, firefighter
 1. the fan trance is on the right of the mechanic##1
 2. the person who growsorchid is the person who growsorchid##1
 3. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
 4. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the electrician##1
 5. the person who growsbellflower is the fan techno##1
 6. the fan country is the doctor##1
 7. the fan country is between the person who growssunflower and the firefighter##2
 8. the person who growsrose is on the left of the fan salsa##1
 9. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
10. the fan ambient is on the right of the freelancer##1
11. the fan salsa is on the right of the fan country##1
12. the electrician is the fan trance##1
13. the fan funk is on the left of the fan country##1
14. the fan funk is on the right of the chef##1
15. the fan trance is on the far right##1
16. the person who growsiris is on the left of the fan techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |    4     |   5    |     6     |    7     |
| Music-Genre   | rock | techno      | funk     | country  | salsa | ambient | trance |
| Flower         | iris  | bellflower | balloon-flower | rose | sunflower | daisy   | orchid  |
| Job     | fisherman   | chef     | firefighter        | doctor  | freelancer   | mechanic       | electrician      |

