.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-4::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: blood-red, ivory, fuchsia, lavender, black, lilac, turquise
The people use 7 different means of transport: taxi, roller, train, bike, tram, van, motorbike
The people have 7 different hobbies: chess, collecting, camping, magic-tricks, dancing, video-games, hiking
 1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left##1
 2. the person driving the van is the person who likes lavender##1
 3. the person who's hobby is camping is the person driving the bike##1
 4. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
 6. the person who likes fuchsia is on the far right##1
 7. the person who likes blood-red is in the middle##1
 8. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the van##1
 9. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person driving the taxi##1
10. the person who's hobby is chess is the person who likes black##1
11. the person driving the train is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
12. the person who likes ivory is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
13. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far right##1
14. the person driving the motorbike is between the person driving the train and the person driving the bike##2
15. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |    3     |    4    |     5      |     6      |     7     |
| Color          | ivory  | lilac    | black  | blood-red | lavender  | turquise | fuchsia |
