.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-5::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea, 7up, iced-tea, lemonade, water, milk
There 7 different types of food: raspberry, pear, garlic, lemon, apple, broccoli, papaya
The people have 7 different hobbies: writing, traveling, camping, rock-climbing, baking, woodworking, reading
 1. the person eating papaya is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 2. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 3. the person drinking lemonade is the person eating pear##1
 4. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 6. the person eating raspberry is the person drinking water##1
 7. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 8. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person drinking 7up##1
 9. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
10. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person eating raspberry##1
11. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
12. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking coffee##2
13. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
14. the person who's hobby is writing is the person eating apple##1
15. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
16. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person eating lemon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |     5      |     6      |     7     |
| Beverage           | iced-tea | 7up    | milk    | coffee  | lemonade | water | tea |
| Food   | lemon      | papaya | garlic | broccoli | pear    | raspberry | apple    |
| Hobby     | rock-climbing     | traveling      | baking    | reading    | camping  | woodworking       | writing  |

