 7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the fan rock##1
 8. the fan salsa is on the right of the fan rock##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the fan indie##1
10. the fan salsa is the person driving the airplane##1
11. the person who's birthday is in december is the person driving the helicopter##1
12. the fan soul is on the far left##1
13. the person driving the train is the fan reggae##1
14. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1
15. the fan jazz is on the far right##1
16. the fan salsa is between the person driving the skateboard and the person who's birthday is in december##2

